		<title>狗狗因長相醜遲遲無人領養！收容所幽默發文為牠迎來新生 </title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/09/23/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e5%9b%a0%e9%95%b7%e7%9b%b8%e9%86%9c%e9%81%b2%e9%81%b2%e7%84%a1%e4%ba%ba%e9%a0%98%e9%a4%8a%ef%bc%81%e6%94%b6%e5%ae%b9%e6%89%80%e5%b9%bd%e9%bb%98%e7%99%bc%e6%96%87%e7%82%ba%e7%89%a0/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 洪瑜蓉]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 23 Sep 2025 06:03:55 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
